{"tid":1036653,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"睇完supper moment有感","createTime":"2019-02-25T11:13:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T12:55:21.000Z","uid":117460,"like":84,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"361c9289ee86e50b5fd5b6b672b1a4497d396727","tid":1036653,"uid":117460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T11:13:11.000Z","msg":"自問睇過好多演唱會，覺得suppermoment絕對係香港眾歌手中，喺舞台上最top既一個單位。<br />\n<br />\n不論係唱功，舞台運用，感染力，都係首屈一指。<br />\n<br />\n明白有啲人會覺得佢地啲歌MK，啱細佬聽。我只可以話，佢地既歌喺YouTube，JOOX, Spotify, KKbox播出黎，同比起唱live 絕對係兩回事。<br />\n<br />\n強烈建議未睇過suppermoment live既人去睇一次，你絕對會對佢地改觀，嗰種感染力係香港好多好多年無見過。<br />\n<br />\n好多時話人唱live唱到好似cd咁係讚佢地，但suppermoment 既live 係絕對比佢地出既任何一隻cd同mv精彩。<br />\n<br />\n利申: 非打手，睇完佢地live好surprised系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f014bea6b7495d9aea418ac3775ffcf7adc7fe1","tid":1036653,"uid":130056,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T11:24:21.000Z","msg":"好心主音咪撚食煙啦"},{"pid":"4f4ce71169facea1df629f34daf898a787a34be5","tid":1036653,"uid":36008,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T11:26:48.000Z","msg":"一樣，本身都喺CD聽晒Supper啲歌但未聽過live而且都鍾意佢哋啲偏門歌<br />\n聽到咜叱佢哋唱《撼動》，真係勁到...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即刻決定去澳門睇， 果然冇令我失望<br />\n成隊都好爆，特別係《不要死在崇拜裡》<br />\nSunny又好識帶氣氛，好有舞台風範，真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"837b32699ff8aa8fc5eee51a0fa14743f2f8a379","tid":1036653,"uid":61736,"like":15,"dislike":5,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T11:28:00.000Z","msg":"每次睇完都會好滿足，同儲夠力量面對工作上嘅奇人怪事。<br />\n<br />\n每次Sunny多謝Gary都好想喊。佢一定好驕傲。<br />\n<br />\n利申：打手，由九展一直走到澳門。期待佢哋走得更遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" cl